OL,5, Victims of the infected blood scandal  
OL,6, should receive compensation            
OL,7, "immediately", a lawyer representing   
OL,8, about 1,500 claimants has said.        
OL,10,FA judge said on Friday that provisional
OL,11,Fcompensation of #100,000 should be paid
OL,12,Fto the more than 4,000 surviving       
OL,13,Fvictims as quickly as possible.        
OL,15,FLawyer Des Collins said payment must be
OL,16,Fmade within "days or weeks" and he will
OL,17,Fbe stepping up pressure from Monday.   
OL,19,FThe government has said it will        
OL,20,Furgently consider any recommendations. 
